Description.Name: Chain Attack: Frost Pact
Ether Veil: Gushing Spring
Description.Desc:
When Decibel Rating reaches <color=#FFFFFF>[Maximum]</color>, landing the final hit with <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace]</color>, <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack: Frost Coil]</color>, <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack: Glacial Crush]</color>, or <color=#FFFFFF>[Chain Attack: Frost Pact]</color> will consume 3000 Decibels and activate <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color>. While <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color> is active, all squad members' max HP increases by 5% for 30 seconds. Repeated triggers extend the duration, up to 300 seconds;
When Yidhari is under <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color>, <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Frostbite Embrace]</color>'s charging speed and HP consumption rate during charging are increased.

1.Name: The past sinks into the abyss
1.Desc: Yidhari's <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack]</color> consumes 10 less Adrenaline; after using <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack]</color> and with sufficient Adrenaline, hold the "Basic Attack" or "Special Attack" button to skip HP recovery and immediately chain into <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack: Glacial Crush]</color>. Each additional <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack]</color> increases the HP recovery of the final <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack: Glacial Crush]</color> by 100%; Yidhari's <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack]</color> and <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack]</color> ignore 15% of target's <color=#98EFF0>Ice RES</color>.

2.Name: Who stands here lost in thought?
2.Desc: Yidhari's CRIT DMG is increased by 40%; after successfully triggering <color=#FFFFFF>[Frost Trace]</color> or <color=#FFFFFF>[Pursuit Crush]</color>, continuously regenerates Adrenaline at 0.5 points per second for up to 30 seconds, repeated triggers reset the duration.

4.Name: Blooming in Silence
4.Desc: In <color=#FFFFFF>[Core Passive: Dreamscape Collection]</color>, when the squad's HP decreases, Yidhari gains 15% more Decibels; while in <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color>, Yidhari's maximum HP is additionally increased by 5%.

6.Name: Dreams of Peace at Last
6.Desc: When Yidhari consumes Decibels to activate <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Gushing Spring]</color>, she gains <color=#FFFFFF>[Enlightenment]</color> for 30 seconds; During <color=#FFFFFF>[Enlightenment]</color>, Yidhari's Sheer DMG is increased by 30%, and the first fatal damage received won't kill her, with HP reduced to 1 at minimum. For 5 seconds, she won't die from fatal damage and continuously recovers 25% HP.
